Log-Log4perl-Appender-SpreadSession version 0.03
================================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Spread::Session
  Log::Log4perl

